		<name>Al Zour Refinery</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<li>🏢 Owner: <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Kuwait Petroleum Corporation</span></span><br></li><li>⚙️ Capacity: <b>~615,000 bpd</b><br></li><li>🧪 Specialisation: Low-sulfur fuels (IMO compliant)<br></li><li>📏 Scale: One of newest mega-refineries<br></li><div><br></div><p>👉 <b>Al Zour = “heavy crude cleaner”</b><br></p><ul><li>Takes <b>dirty heavy crude</b><br></li><li><div>Turns it into:<br></div><ul><li>Clean fuel oil<br></li><li>Low-sulfur diesel/jet<br></li></ul></li></ul><div><br></div><div><br></div><ul><li>Huge supplier of <b>VLSFO (marine fuel)</b><br></li><li><div>Influences:<br></div><ul><li>Singapore bunker market<br></li></ul></li><li>High volumes → affects <b>regional spreads</b><br></li></ul><div><br></div>]]></description>
