		<Placemark id="03CC2AA86E3EB75AA49C">
		<name>Danube Refinery</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<h1>⚙️ What it is<br></h1><ul><li>Operated by: <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">MOL Group</span></span><br></li><li>Capacity: ~<b>165,000 barrels per day</b> (matches your quote)<br></li></ul><p>👉 It is:<br></p><blockquote><p><b>Hungary’s only major crude oil refinery</b><br></p></blockquote><div><hr><br></div><h1>🛢️ What it does<br></h1><p>Processes crude oil into:<br></p><ul><li>Diesel (ULSD)<br></li><li>Gasoline<br></li><li>Jet fuel<br></li><li>Petrochemical feedstocks<br></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h1>🔗 How it is supplied<br></h1><p>Main crude supply:<br></p><ul><li><b><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Druzhba pipeline</span></span></b> (Russia via Ukraine)<br></li><li><div>Backup:<br></div><ul><li><b><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Adria pipeline</span></span></b><br></li></ul></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h1>⚠️ Why Hungary still imports diesel<br></h1><p>Even with this refinery:<br></p><p>👉 Hungary:<br></p><ul><li>❌ Does NOT produce enough diesel<br></li><li>✔️ Needs imports<br></li></ul><p>Main supplier:<br></p><ul><li><div><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Slovakia</span></span><br></div><ul><li>via the <b>Bratislava refinery (Slovnaft)</b><br></li></ul></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h1>🧠 Why this happens<br></h1><p>Refineries don’t produce equal amounts of all fuels:<br></p><ul><li><div>Danube refinery may:<br></div><ul><li>produce more gasoline<br></li><li>less diesel<br></li></ul></li></ul><p>👉 So Hungary:<br></p><blockquote><p><br></p><div>Exports some products<br></div><div>Imports others (especially diesel)<br></div><p><br></p></blockquote><div><br></div>]]></description>
		<LookAt>
			<longitude>18.89850153628964</longitude>
			<latitude>47.28434477978583</latitude>
