		<Placemark id="0B015372A33EB40D5613">
		<name>Onsan SUPER Refinery</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<li>🏢 Owner: <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">S-Oil</span></span><br></li><li>⚙️ Capacity: <b>~669,000 bpd</b><br></li><li>🧪 Specialisation: Lube base oil, clean fuels<br></li><li>📏 Scale: Advanced conversion refinery<br></li><div><br></div><p>👉 <b>More optimized for high-value clean fuels + lube base oils</b><br></p><ul><li>Very high upgrading capability<br></li><li>Focus on premium products<br></li></ul><div><br></div>]]></description>
		<LookAt>
			<longitude>129.3375233230387</longitude>
