		<name>Bayernoil Refinery Neustadt</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<div>A cornerstone of Germany’s energy landscape, Bayernoil is one of Europe’s largest and most modern refineries, operating across two sites — Neustadt and Vohburg. ￼ VARO holds a majority stake (approximately 51.4%). The refinery processes crude delivered via the Trans-Alpine Pipeline (TAL) from Trieste and the South European Pipeline (SPSE). It supplies Bavaria and southern Germany with fuels and petrochemicals.<br></div>]]></description>
