		<name>Port of Maputo</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<li>Major port in southern Africa<br></li><li>Includes <b>Maputo + Matola industrial terminals</b><br></li><div><br></div><div><br></div><p>Mozambique is a <b>regional distribution and consumption hub</b><br></p><ul><li><div>Receives fuel cargoes and:<br></div><ul><li>Supplies <b>Southern Africa</b><br></li><li>Serves industrial demand<br></li></ul></li><li>Also used for <b>bunkering ships</b><br></li></ul><p>➡️ When Singapore demand weakens:<br></p><ul><li><div>Cargoes are redirected here because:<br></div><ul><li>Strong regional demand<br></li><li>Better margins<br></li></ul></li></ul><div><br></div>]]></description>
