rmal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Stores it in </span></span></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">large tank farms (what you see inland)</span></span></b></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Pumps it to the </span></span></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">long offshore loading jetty</span></span></b></span><br></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 21px;">🔹 Key point:</span></span></b></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">👉 This is historically the </span></span></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">main出口 for Iraqi oil (including Kurdistan flows when allowed)</span></span></b></span><br></p><div><br></div>]]></description>
