		<name>Amsterdam (storage &amp; trading hub) </name>
		<description><![CDATA[<h2>What you find:<br></h2><ul><li>🛢️ Massive <b>tank storage terminals</b><br></li><li>🔄 Fuel <b>blending facilities</b><br></li><li>🚢 Import/export terminals<br></li></ul><h2>Role:<br></h2><blockquote><p><b>Warehouse + trading hub for fuels</b><br></p></blockquote><ul><li>Stores gasoline, diesel, jet fuel<br></li><li>Mixes products to required specs<br></li><li>Sets benchmark prices (ARA pricing)<br></li></ul><p>👉 No major refinery, no large petrochemical complex<br></p><div><br></div>]]></description>
