		<description><![CDATA[<h2>What you find:<br></h2><ul><li>🏭 Refineries (ExxonMobil, TotalEnergies)<br></li><li><div>🧪 Massive <b>petrochemical complexes</b><br></div><ul><li>BASF<br></li><li>INEOS<br></li></ul></li><li>🔥 Steam crackers (key units)<br></li></ul><h2>Role:<br></h2><blockquote><p><b>Turn fuels into chemicals and materials</b><br></p></blockquote><ul><li>Takes refinery outputs (like naphtha)<br></li><li><div>Produces:<br></div><ul><li>plastics<br></li><li>chemicals<br></li><li>industrial materials<br></li></ul></li></ul><div><br></div>]]></description>
