	</Folder>
	<Folder>
		<name>Petrochemical Plants (4)</name>
		<Placemark id="00C02568723EB7B9A5C6">
		<name>MOL Petrochemicals Tiszaújváros</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<div><div>What it does:&nbsp;Uses <b>refinery outputs (like naphtha, propylene)</b><br></div></div><li><div>Turns them into : plastics,&nbsp;industrial chemicals<br></div></li><div><br></div><div>Produces:<br></div><ul><li><ul><li>plastics (polyethylene, polypropylene)<br></li><li>synthetic rubber<br></li><li>chemical intermediates (polyols, propylene, etc.)<br></li></ul></li><li>Part of <b><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">MOL Group</span></span></b><br></li></ul><p>👉 It’s one of MOL’s <b>two main chemical production sites in Hungary</b><br></p><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div>]]></description>
		<LookAt>
			<longitude>21.0491307468206</longitude>
			<latitude>47.89381560823652</latitude>
			<altitude>91.84558328701513</altitude>
			<heading>0</heading>
			<tilt>0</tilt>
			<gx:fovy>35</gx:fovy>
			<range>6673.615556481527</range>
			<altitudeMode>absolute</altitudeMode>
		</LookAt>
		<styleUrl>#__managed_style_1F52009F934081E89039</styleUrl>
		<Point>
			<coordinates>21.02832293073626,47.89420784451342,93.98698311388492</coordinates>
		</Point>
	</Placemark>
		<Placemark id="0C008C1AB53EB8584258">
		<name>Dow Terneuzen</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<h1>🧪 What it is<br></h1><ul><li>Operated by: <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Dow</span></span><br></li><li><div>Often referred to as:<br></div><ul><li><b>Dow Terneuzen</b><br></li><li><b>Dow Benelux site</b><br></li></ul></li></ul><p>👉 It’s one of <b>Dow’s largest production sites outside the US</b><br></p><div><hr><br></div><h1>⚙️ What happens there<br></h1><p>It’s a <b>fully integrated petrochemical complex</b>, producing:<br></p><ul><li>Plastics (polyethylene, polystyrene)<br></li><li>Chemical intermediates<br></li><li>Industrial materials<br></li></ul><p>👉 Think:<br></p><blockquote><p>Raw hydrocarbons → chemicals → plastics → industrial products<br></p></blockquote><div><hr><br></div><h1>🌍 Why it’s so big<br></h1><ul><li>Located inside <b><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">North Sea Port</span></span></b><br></li><li><div>Connected to:<br></div><ul><li>Antwerp petrochemical cluster<br></li><li>Rotterdam refining hub<br></li></ul></li><li><div>Access to:<br></div><ul><li>Ships (via canal)<br></li><li>Pipelines<br></li><li>European markets<br></li></ul></li></ul><div><br></div>]]></description>
		<LookAt>
			<longitude>3.787764908666296</longitude>
			<latitude>51.34081760073316</latitude>
			<altitude>3.924655696200103</altitude>
