		<Placemark id="088695B4F83EB745CF80">
		<name>TurkStream</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<ul><li>Starts in <b>Russia (near Anapa, Black Sea coast)</b><br></li><li>Runs <b>~930 km under the Black Sea</b> to Turkey<br></li><li>Comes ashore at <b>Kıyıköy (northwest Turkey)</b><br></li><li><div>Two خطوط (pipes):<br></div><ul><li>Line 1 → supplies Turkey<br></li><li>Line 2 → continues to Europe<br></li></ul></li></ul><p>👉 Since <b>2025</b>, this is basically <b>the only remaining pipeline route for Russian gas into Europe</b> after Ukraine transit stopped<br></p><p>This extension tu europe is often called <b><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Balkan Stream gas pipeline</span></span></b>:<br></p><p>Route:<br></p><ol><li>Turkey → Bulgaria<br></li><li>Bulgaria → Serbia<br></li><li>Serbia → Hungary (entry near <b>Horgoš border</b>)<br></li></ol><ul><li>Total length ~880 km<br></li><li><div>Supplies countries like:<br></div><ul><li>Bulgaria<br></li><li>Serbia<br></li><li>Hungary<br></li><li>Slovakia (via connections)<br></li></ul></li></ul><p>👉 This is why Hungary gets <b>~60% of its gas via this southern route</b> (as your quote says).<br></p><h3>Key points:<br></h3><ul><li>Hungary <b>bypasses Ukraine completely</b> now<br></li><li><div>It relies on a route controlled by:<br></div><ul><li>Russia (gas supply)<br></li><li>Turkey (transit gatekeeper)<br></li></ul></li><li>This gives <b>political leverage</b> to both<br></li></ul><p>👉 Meanwhile:<br></p><ul><li>EU wants to reduce Russian gas<br></li><li>Hungary signs LNG deals to diversify<br></li></ul><div><br></div>]]></description>
		<LookAt>
			<longitude>28.09960805764119</longitude>
			<latitude>41.65313032189176</latitude>
			<altitude>-2.970003748004949</altitude>
			<heading>0</heading>
			<tilt>0</tilt>
			<gx:fovy>35</gx:fovy>
			<range>12343.92438365961</range>
			<altitudeMode>absolute</altitudeMode>
		</LookAt>
		<styleUrl>#__managed_style_0AFE3B87624081E89038</styleUrl>
		<LineString>
			<coordinates>
				37.31671591658544,44.89017894953972,0 28.0773679183663,41.65015286639992,0 
			</coordinates>
		</LineString>
	</Placemark>
