		<Placemark id="089231CDAD3ED2D9E710">
		<name>Mozambique–South Africa Petroleum Products Pipeline</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<h2>Key details<br></h2><ul><li><b>Start:</b> Matola (near Maputo, Mozambique)<br></li><li><b>End:</b> Inland fuel distribution system in South Africa (Mpumalanga / Gauteng region)<br></li><li><b>Length:</b> ~500 km<br></li><li><b>Product:</b> Refined fuels (diesel, petrol, fuel oil — not crude)<br></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h2>🔹 Important clarification<br></h2><p>This pipeline:<br></p><ul><li>Does <b>not</b> have a widely used commercial brand name (like some major pipelines)<br></li><li><div>Is often described functionally as:<br></div><ul><li><b>Maputo–Kendal pipeline</b><br></li><li>or <b>Matola–South Africa fuel pipeline</b><br></li></ul></li></ul><p>👉 So you may see <b>different names depending on the source</b><br></p><div><hr><br></div><h2>🔹 Don’t confuse it with this one<br></h2><p>There is also a better-known pipeline:<br></p><p>👉 <b><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">ROMPCO Gas Pipeline</span></span></b><br></p><ul><li>Carries <b>natural gas</b>, not oil products<br></li><li>Goes to Secunda<br></li><li>Much more documented and visible in maps<br></li></ul><div><hr><br></div><h2>🔹 Link to your article<br></h2><p>The pipeline we’re discussing is important because:<br></p><ul><li>Fuel cargoes diverted to <b>Mozambique (Matola)</b><br></li><li><div>Can then be:<br></div><ul><li>Stored<br></li><li>Or sent inland via this pipeline<br></li></ul></li></ul><p>👉 Supplying <b>Southern African demand instead of Singapore</b><br></p><div><br></div>]]></description>
		<LookAt>
			<longitude>29.2292456491966</longitude>
			<latitude>-26.24425345884732</latitude>
			<altitude>1590.101526111981</altitude>
			<heading>0</heading>
			<tilt>0</tilt>
			<gx:fovy>35</gx:fovy>
			<range>135552.9490196519</range>
			<altitudeMode>absolute</altitudeMode>
		</LookAt>
		<styleUrl>#__managed_style_0867C338994081E89028</styleUrl>
		<LineString>
			<coordinates>
				32.49960800162238,-25.95937431606155,0 31.94044843041256,-25.45388269156171,0 30.9658917053511,-25.47056644272303,0 29.04486522022537,-26.05031795979596,0 29.15584442063949,-26.54838320055666,0 
			</coordinates>
		</LineString>
	</Placemark>
		<Placemark id="0B66F491DC3F2390C62D">
		<name>Caspian Pipeline Consortium</name>
		<description><![CDATA[<p style="margin: 0px 0px 16.4px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 23px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family:TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"><span class="size" style="font-size:23px">The</span></span></b></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family:TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"><span class="size" style="font-size:21px">main export route for Kazakhstan’s oil</span></span></b></span><br></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span class="size" style="font-size:20px">Carries </span></span></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family:TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"><span class="size" style="font-size:20px">~80%+ of Kazakhstan’s crude exports</span></span></b></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span class="size" style="font-size:20px">Connects inland oil fields to global markets</span></span></span><br></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(128, 128, 128); min-height: 13.8px;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16.4px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 23px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family:TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"><span class="size" style="font-size:23px">🔹 A</span></span></b></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family:TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"><span class="size" style="font-size:21px">direct link to the sea</span></span></b></span><br></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span class="size" style="font-size:20px">Starts in western Kazakhstan</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span class="size" style="font-size:20px">Ends at the Black Sea near Novorossiysk</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span class="size" style="font-size:20px">Allows landlocked oil to reach tankers</span></span></span><br></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span class="size" style="font-size:20px">👉 Without it, Kazakhstan would struggle to export oil efficiently.</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(128, 128, 128); min-height: 13.8px;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16.4px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 23px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family:TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"><span class="size" style="font-size:23px">🔹 A</span></span></b></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family:TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"><span class="size" styl