	</Placemark>
		<Placemark id="0D7B0B4A7E3F6266D6D6">
		<name>NATO pipeline </name>
		<description><![CDATA[<p style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">The NATO pipeline network — officially called the Central Europe Pipeline System — is one of the largest and most strategic military fuel transportation systems in the world. It is a vast underground network of pipelines, storage depots, pumping stations, refineries, and airport connections built to guarantee fuel supply for NATO military operations across Western and Central Europe.</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 14.9px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 24px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 24px;">What the pipeline actually transports</span></span></b></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">The system mainly transports:</span></span></span><br></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Jet fuel (JP-8 / Jet A-1)</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Diesel</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Gasoline</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Military refined petroleum products</span></span></span><br></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">It does </span></span></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">not</span></span></b></span><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;"> transport crude oil like long-distance oil trunklines.</span></span></span><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 12px;"><br> </span></span></span><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">It transports </span></span></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">refined fuels</span></span></b></span><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;"> ready to be consumed by:</span></span></span></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">fighter jets</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">military aircraft</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">tanks</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">naval support infrastructure</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">civilian airports connected to the network</span></span></span><br></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(128, 128, 128); min-height: 13.8px;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16.1px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 30px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 30px;">Why it was built</span></span></b></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">The network was created during the Cold War after NATO realized that:</span></span></span><br></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">tanker trucks were vulnerable,</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">rail transport could be destroyed,</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">ports could be blocked,</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">and air forces required uninterrupted fuel supply during a Soviet invasion scenario.</span></span></span><br></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">The idea was therefore:</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">create an underground fuel “circulatory system” across Europe.</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Construction began in the 1950s.</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(128, 128, 128); min-height: 13.8px;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 16.1px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 30px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 30px;">Physical description of the system</span></span></b></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">The CEPS is not one single pipeline.</span></span></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">It is a </span></span></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">continental-scale integrated fuel logistics network</span></span></b></span><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;"> composed of:</span></span></span><br></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-width: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-